.name
ShadowMaker
.author
Stephen Lebans 
.version
1.5
.description
Demo version of an Intuition based Font shadow generator.  In seconds you
can convert your favorite fonts into color fonts with professional video
shadows built right in.  The only restriction for this demo is that the
final font height at SAVE times must be less than 40 pixels in height.  An
update to version on disk 428.  
